Protecting your privacy is a priority for us. Our privacy policy explains how information is collected, used and disclosed by Augustine Institute, Inc. with respect to your access and use of Amen's services, whether through our website (located at
https://amenapp.org
) or Amen’s mobile application (referred to below as “Amen”). This Privacy Policy does not apply to any third-party websites, services or applications, even if they are accessible through our Services. If you have questions regarding our Privacy Policy, please contact
help@amenapp.org
.